On Mon, 10 Dec 2001, Dave C. Bolen wrote:


sounds like an AFM problem, check the plug on the back of the Air Flow
Meter it could be working loose.

see that the flappper inside is moving freely.

there is fairly long segment in archives on checking the PC trace in the
AFM which occasionally wear out.

